Class Recording

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--Recording
Direct Known Subclasses:
MusicRecording, VideoRecording
public abstract class Recording
extends Object
implements Comparable

This class represents a Recording. It describes the recording title, price, category, imageName and duration.

Subclasses must implement the method getDuration() to return the total duration for the recording.

Author:
App Development Team
